      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="ml-3">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-purple-800">How to Test Drag and Drop</h3>
      <ol class="mt-2 text-sm text-purple-700 list-decimal pl-5">
        <li>Click and hold on any tab</li>
        <li>Drag it to a new position in the tab bar</li>
        <li>Release to drop the tab in its new position</li>
      </ol>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-purple-700">
        This feature allows users to organize their tabs in a way that makes sense for their workflow.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

